[Miscellaneous Codes\Insanely Quick EXP Gain Modifier (Kills)]
author=Pyriel
description=
patch=1,EE,201B1544,extended,34020000

[Item Level 100]
author=bungholio
description=Set it to whatever you want.  It does go higher than level
100.
patch=1,EE,10384CAA,extended,00000064

[Item World Current Enemy Level]
author=bungholio
description=I just set it to 0 to keep them at their easiest level.  Or set it as high as you&#039;d like for a challenge.
patch=1,EE,00384CC8,extended,00000000

[Item World Enemies Start With 0 SP]
author=bungholio
description=
patch=1,EE,20256C3C,extended,34020000

[Item World Neutrals Start With 0 SP]
author=bungholio
description=Neutrals are the ones with yellow health bars, like geopanels, specialists, and treasure chests.
patch=1,EE,20238DC0,extended,34020000

[Item World Stage]
author=bungholio
description=It&#039;s useful to skip around.  You can go straight to level 99
if you want to.
patch=1,EE,00384CB6,extended,00000000

