[Level Select]
author=bungholio
description=Borrowed Pyriel&#039;s joker. Just go to that girl to select a level, select a chapter (but not a level yet), and before you pick a level, press one of those 3 button combinations to get a list. Pick whatever one you want. A lot of them are listed twice, the second one of each level is that Dark World version. I tried &quot;Promotion Exam1&quot; and the game got stuck at a loading screen. The first few stages are probably worlds rather than actual levels, so you end up in an empty room and need to quit. I&#039;m not sure how to get to those worlds the normal way. It isn&#039;t saveable or anything like that, use at your own risk though when choosing a level you&#039;ve never seen before.
patch=1,EE,A116CF19,extended,492E6739
patch=1,EE,C14BB924,extended,51A76D17
patch=1,EE,A0716005,extended,70D78F01
patch=1,EE,B0000001,extended,32726466
patch=1,EE,30400000,extended,0192D0AC
