[Population 8]
author=bungholio
description=Normally items can only have a maximum of 8 in this game.
If you set it higher, it starts interpreting values for other
codes like stats as specialist info.  Not really a bad thing,
but you can&#039;t pick both, you either set the stats you want
or change the stats to specific specialist data.
patch=1,EE,00384CC5,extended,00000008

